noprefix "false"

\end_inset

对
\begin_inset Formula $\delta\Phi_{\text{min},k}$
\end_inset

求微分，并且利用
\begin_inset Formula $m_{ij}^{2}=m_{ji}^{2}$
\end_inset

，导致矩阵方程
\begin_inset Formula 
\[
M^{2}\delta\vec{\Phi}_{\text{min}}=\vec{0}
\]

\end_inset

这里的等于零同上。将EQ
\begin_inset CommandInset ref
LatexCommand ref
reference "eq:2.21"
plural "false"
caps "false"
noprefix "false"

\end_inset

中对任意
\begin_inset Formula $\varepsilon_{a}$
\end_inset

的变分插入，
\begin_inset Formula $\delta\vec{\Phi}_{\text{min}}=-i\varepsilon_{a}T_{a}\vec{\Phi}_{\text{min}}$
\end_inset

，我们总结到
